    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to the rear wheels via a limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on structural integrity, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings to preserve the factory-spec kinematics. Engine health is a priority; the rod bearings have been addressed, and the valvetrain remains crisp. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited driving, the performance envelope remains wide, supported by a communicative steering rack and a firm, predictable suspension setup. A driver-focused machine for those who value mechanical pedigree over a concours finish.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
